<html>
<body>
<section class="mbr-box mbr-section mbr-section--relative mbr-section--fixed-size mbr-section--full-height mbr-section--bg-adapted mbr-parallax-background" id="header1-25" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('otherindex-1920x1080-15.png') %> );">
    <div class="mbr-box__magnet mbr-box__magnet--sm-padding mbr-box__magnet--center-left">

        <div class="mbr-box__container mbr-section__container container">
            <div class="mbr-box mbr-box--stretched"><div class="mbr-box__magnet mbr-box__magnet--center-left">
                <div class="row"><div class=" col-sm-6">
                    <div class="mbr-hero animated fadeInUp">

                        <p class="mbr-hero__subtext"></p>
                    </div>

                </div></div>
            </div></div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="mbr-section mbr-section--relative mbr-section--fixed-size" id="content4-26" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">


    <div class="mbr-section__container container mbr-section__container--std-top-padding" style="padding-top: 93px;">
     <div class="mbr-header--left mbr-header--std-padding">
                        <%= render_breadcrumbs %>
                        </div>
                         <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--center mbr-header--std-padding">

                            <h2 class="mbr-section__header" id="contacts1-15">Alternative Loan Options</h2>
                            <hr>
        <div class="mbr-section__row row">
            <div class="mbr-section__col col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-sm-6">

                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                    <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--reduce mbr-header--center mbr-header--wysiwyg">
                        <h3 class="mbr-header__text">FIXED RATE LOANS</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--last" style="padding-bottom: 93px;">
                    <div class="mbr-article mbr-article--wysiwyg">
                        <p>Your rate will never change.  Your payment will never change.  Even if rates fluctuate in the market. It is that simple.  A fixed rate loan is the most secure option and usually the most popular, because you will always know what your payment will be, throughout the full duration of your loan.  We offer 30, 25, 20, 15, and 10 year fixed rate loan options.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="mbr-section__col col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-sm-6">

                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                    <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--reduce mbr-header--center mbr-header--wysiwyg">
                        <h3 class="mbr-header__text">FHA LOANS</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--last" style="padding-bottom: 93px;">
                    <div class="mbr-article mbr-article--wysiwyg">
                        <p>These loans are federally insured.  They can offer financing for people who are looking for a smaller down payment or have struggled obtaining conventional financing. Typically, FHA loans have flexible terms, they are popular among first-time home buyers and those with a few blemishes on their credit report.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="clearfix visible-sm-block"></div>
            <div class="mbr-section__col col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-sm-6">

                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                    <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--reduce mbr-header--center mbr-header--wysiwyg">
                        <h3 class="mbr-header__text">HOME IMPROVEMENT LOANS</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--last" style="padding-bottom: 93px;">
                    <div class="mbr-article mbr-article--wysiwyg">
                        <p>Looking to do alterations, remodeling, or structural improvements?  Our Home Improvement Loans allow your mortgage balance to exceed the sale price or current value of the home, so you can take out extra money for upgrades.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="mbr-section__col col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-sm-6">

                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                    <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--reduce mbr-header--center mbr-header--wysiwyg">
                        <h3 class="mbr-header__text">JUMBO LOANS</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--last" style="padding-bottom: 93px;">
                    <div class="mbr-article mbr-article--wysiwyg">
                        <p>Conventional loans are not always enough to cover the financing for high-priced homes. A Jumbo mortgage is a securitized mortgage (by one our lenders).  Typically, it can be used to finance up to 85 percent of your new home (with no private mortgage insurance).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>



        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mbr-box__container mbr-section__container container">
        <div class="mbr-box mbr-box--stretched"><div class="mbr-box__magnet mbr-box__magnet--center-center">
            <div class="row"><div class=" col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2" style="padding-bottom: 60px;">

                <div class="mbr-buttons btn-inverse mbr-buttons--center"><a class="mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-lg btn-info" href="<%= asset_path(new_apply_path) %>">APPLY NOW</a> <a class="mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="/">Back</a></div>

    </div>

</div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
